  symmetry x
  polygon 31 39 38 31 46 39 38 47 steeldeep
  polygon 34 39 38 35 42 39 38 43 oxblooddeep
  line 31 39 38 31 silveredge
  line 38 31 46 39 steelhi
  line 46 39 38 47 steelhi
  line 38 47 31 39 silveredge
